title: Strömsholmens
description:
Five and ten camps are an activity designed to weld together friends and groups at business conferences or kick-offs with school and work. Marholmen also has a long tradition of tiocamp. Here is nature available, therefore we have adapted our tentacle to the theme of "wilderness" and have done our activities for both the brain and the body. You participate in branches like excitement, archery, stocking and ship bowling.

You gather around our campfire at Strömsholmen before and after a successful campaign.

Price: 390 kr / per ink VAT (312 kr / per ex moms) Min. deb.10 pers.
